title: Seishun Danshi Shugei Club
description: The craft's club president at Seishun Boy's High is led by an exceptional beauty, Kurone Kanae, who is known throughout the school body. A mid-year enrollment student, Matsuda Mirayoshi, suddenly decides to join the club upon setting his eyes on Kurone. After his application is accepted, Matsuda will have several challenges to face!
